ActCanada Post Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of ALAIN SANS CARTIER of L'Ancienne-Lorette, Quebec, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Denyse Chicoyne.
